OL,3,CJob Centre security guards stage two-
OL,4,Cday walkout over pay
OL,6,FJob Centre security guards across the
OL,7,Fregion are walking out in a dispute
OL,8,Fover pay and conditions.
OL,10,FPicket lines had been put in place at
OL,11,FNewcastle, Middlesbrough and York.
OL,13,FThey joined 1,400 guards across the UK
OL,14,Fwho are taking part in the two-day
OL,15,Findustrial action.
OL,17,FThe GMB union has said that 90% of the
OL,18,Fguards, who are employed by G4S, are
OL,19,Fpaid the minimum wage. This is despite
OL,20,Fthem regularly facing attacks, and
OL,21,Fabuse at work.
