OL,3,CJob Centre security guards stage two-
OL,4,Cday walkout over pay
OL,6,FEamon O'Hearn, GMB National Officer,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Job Centre security guards are
OL,8,Fpunched, attacked and savaged in the
OL,9,Fneck by dogs ` just for carrying out
OL,10,Ftheir duties.
OL,12,F"Yet 90% of them struggle to get by on
OL,13,Fthe minimum wage, while G4S trouser
OL,14,Fmillions from the DWP.
OL,16,F"It's abhorrent and these strikes will
OL,17,Fkeep escalating unless G4S agrees to
OL,18,Fpay them a wage they can live on."
