OL,3,CJob Centre security guards stage two-
OL,4,Cday walkout over pay
OL,6,FA spokesperson from G4S said: "Our
OL,7,Fdedicated security colleagues do a
OL,8,Fgreat job, sometimes in difficult
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,F"We urge the GMB to present our offer
OL,12,Fto our employees, which is both above
OL,13,Fminimum wage and inflation. We are
OL,14,Fkeen to bring this dispute to an
OL,15,Famicable conclusion.J"Our contingency
OL,16,Fplans, agreed in partnership with DWP
OL,17,Fhave proved highly effective in
OL,18,Fmaintaining a full service, and we
OL,19,Fcontinue to adapt them to ensure the
OL,20,Fsafety of DWP locations, employees and
OL,21,Fthe service users."
